Package: GBJ
Type: Package
Title: The Generalized Berk-Jones Statistic for Set-Based Inference
Version: 0.2.1
Date: 2016-10-05
Authors@R: person("Ryan", "Sun", email = "ryansun.work@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Computes the Generalized Berk-Jones (GBJ) statistic for set-based inference on multiple hypotheses.  Also includes routines to compute the Generalized Higher Criticism (GHC), Higher Criticism (HC), Berk-Jones (BJ), and Minimum p-value (minP) tests.  See vignette for explanations and examples.
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 0.12.7),
    stats,
    BH
LinkingTo: Rcpp
License: GPL-3
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
